## Scripts

{{#if (eq packageManager "bun")}}
- `bun run dev` - start the Astro dev server
- `bun run build` - build for production
- `bun run preview` - preview the production build
- `bun run astro` - run Astro CLI commands
{{else}}
{{#if (eq packageManager "pnpm")}}
- `pnpm dev` - start the Astro dev server
- `pnpm build` - build for production
- `pnpm preview` - preview the production build
- `pnpm astro` - run Astro CLI commands
{{else}}
{{#if (eq packageManager "npm")}}
- `npm run dev` - start the Astro dev server
- `npm run build` - build for production
- `npm run preview` - preview the production build
- `npm run astro` - run Astro CLI commands
{{else}}
- `npm run dev` or `pnpm dev` or `bun run dev` - start the Astro dev server
- `npm run build` or `pnpm build` or `bun run build` - build for production
- `npm run preview` or `pnpm preview` or `bun run preview` - preview the production build
- `npm run astro` or `pnpm astro` or `bun run astro` - run Astro CLI commands
{{/if}}
